  <brief_title>Early Markers of Radiation-Induced Cardiac Injury in Hodgkin Lymphoma Treated With Radiation Therapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>UFPTI 1431 - HL02: Investigating Early Markers of Radiation-Induced Cardiac Injury in Hodgkin Lymphoma Survivors Treated With Either Photon or Proton Radiation</official_title>
