      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Completed radiation and chemotherapy treatment for Hodgkin lymphoma involving the
             mediastinum.

